                            <date notBefore="0508" notAfter="0511" calendar="Gregorian">Between 508 and 511</date>, <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/51">Severus</persName>wrote a letter to<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2417">Solon</persName>concerning his ordination, piety, and relationship to unorthodox bishops.
                        </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/letters http://syriaca.org/keyword/ordination http://syriaca.org/keyword/heresy http://syriaca.org/keyword/anathema http://syriaca.org/keyword/bishops http://syriaca.org/keyword/sanctity"/>
