            </div>
            <div uri="http://syriaca.org/spear/3012-31" resp="#syoung">
                <listEvent>
                    <event>
                        <desc>
                            To defend his belief in the ordination of priests by those outside of a particular diocese,<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/51">Severus</persName> appeals to the examples of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/376">Basil</persName>during the controversy surrounding<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2486">Arius</persName>, and <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/511">Gregory the Theologian</persName>.
                        </desc>
